ear All,We’re happy to announce the launch of Wiki Loves Ramadan 2025, an annual international campaign dedicated to celebrating and preserving Islamic cultures and history through the power of Wikipedia.
ve contributor to the Local Wikipedia, you are specially invited to participate in the launch.
This year’s campaign will be launched for you to join us write, edit, and improve articles that showcase the richness and diversity of Islamic traditions, history, and culture.To get started, visit the campaign page for details, resources, and guidelines: Wiki Loves Ramadan 2025.Add your community here, and organized Wiki Loves Ramadan 2025 in your local language.
Wikipedian, your contributions matter. Together, we can ensure Islamic cultures and traditions are well-represented and accessible to all.
Feel free to invite your community and friends too.
Kindly reach out if you have any questions or need support as you prepare to participate.
